server can handle multiple client using fork...a tcp connection...minimum of 3 clients
server receives alphabet from of minimum size 5 characters...
server sends client a menu "
1) upper case all charecters
2)lower case all charecters
3) count total no. of charecters
4) reverse the charecters 
"
server receives what action to perform from client and then send the output to client..
the client receives the final result and print it.